From the balance sheet provided:
- Accounts Payable had an initial amount of 0.00 on 2023-12-31
- Accounts Payable had an end amount of 0.00 on 2024-02-05

Therefore, both the initial and end values for amounts owed for goods or services purchased on credit are 0.00.
